get.description:
Get job containers statistics by its id.

Format of the response:

.. code-block:: json

{
  "containers": {
      "<job-subtask-1-name>": {
          "name": "<job-subtask-1-container-name>",
          "exit_codes": {
              "<exit-code-1>" : <number of containers exited with exit-code-1>,
              "<exit-code-2>" : <number of containers exited with exit-code-2>,
              ...
          }
      },
      ...
  }
}


:param job_id: id of the job to retrieve
